Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這感覺不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:11.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,確實不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:11.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:14.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我感覺很好「光榮天使號」列車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.63,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺像是潑婦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且 你也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我只是想說很華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:20.79,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要抱怨你也說一個唄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那就「真我號」列車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:28.54,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不如用淺顯易懂的「池袋特快號」怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這也差不了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 快的感覺太明顯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留你有什麼好點子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「遠地點號」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼G
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,Apogee
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:43.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,月球或其它衛星 在繞地飛行時與地球最遠的距離點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感覺好時尚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不也挺好的 遠地點號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:47.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你現在就是「阿波爺爺」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留是喜歡星空和宇宙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:53.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,首聞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是我 是葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香她無論到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感覺都會拿著繪本塗塗抹抹的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說起來葉香她 為什麼會去池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且還是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:12.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對對 就這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我之前也是很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:18.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香一個人獨自做什麼事的印象 我是完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:19.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.97,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這樣的葉香竟然一個人前往池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:24.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不僅奇怪 還不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且還帶有一絲神秘感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:27.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋那還有什麼特色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:33.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,還有就是 書店劇場水族館
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:35.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 她是會去那裡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.25,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺她根本不會去那些地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香雖然從小就和她在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但她也不是自力更生的類型呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一直都在人面前笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感覺 我們對葉香的了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,並不知道很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,別這樣 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.53,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要說讓人寂寞的話呀
Comment: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.80,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,地球和月球相距最遠的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,兩者之間的距離有四十萬 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 五分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,時間太短了 每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:39.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這個烤熟以後撒上鹽會很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,剩下的等會還能用來做竹筍飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇它嘔吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要是貓的話經常性嘔吐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是從吾野離開後這是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吃了什麼奇怪的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要是波奇出了事該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,到了池袋以後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還得讓波奇來幫忙找葉香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,能夠追蹤到葉香氣味的只有波奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:14.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,所以 絕對要你平平安安的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇它現在多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 波奇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,在我們小時候就一直和波奇一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是說有十三四歲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇敲 都成老爺爺犬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是誰提到小雪奶奶年齡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這種話一說就生氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這和那時不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:37.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要是波奇死了的話 我心也就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大概沒什麼問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留完全沒什麼說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你不擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,帶上波奇的明明是靜留你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 等會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我沒有強迫它跟我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是波奇它自己跟來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還說這話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們現在能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,雖然並不是靜留你強迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但你要說我們只是跟著你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算是對的也不近人情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這些 我之前也有說到過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,聽我說 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香她到底為什麼會去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留你肯定知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼要現在問我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.20,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,現在問不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不想說太多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不想說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留對葉香 說了或是做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 葉香她生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香哭的樣子完全無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,實際上我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你肯定做了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就只是說了一句「是嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸嘿 好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸嘿 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,宇宙 就是我們所在的宇宙對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香竟然是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我完全不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這個該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,天文學 是天文學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.89,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不過 我想做的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.10,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,研製未來的行星探測衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.76,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,規劃宇宙太空站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.35,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,以及控制技術的開發系…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 才能成為做成這些事的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.85,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:25.23,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,上大學 努力學習 寫論文什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,有機會再申請研究機構的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,申請 就這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,嗯 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這難道不是困難重重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.21,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.71,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我並不厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,宇宙 衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這些要高攀成就的 我從未放在心上想過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或許是我想都不敢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現實地考慮一下 自己會成為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:03.72,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,現實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,哪些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.27,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,畢竟 我只是個普通人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,難道不是非常特別的人才做得到的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 我不是瞧不起葉香你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:21.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 感覺你說的這些遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.33,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,遙不可及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,從吾野去到星辰、宇宙、銀河系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,牛皮吹太大了也會不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必須要在某種程度上接受現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼不正常一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,都不過平凡的人罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再說了 真不需要考慮自己到底有多特別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香也是 你能夠有偉大的想法很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但做不到的時候會很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再說了葉香你 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,什麼怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然你變得沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我說了奇怪的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.08,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.92,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我想原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這樣是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你要是不喜歡我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,直接說出來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:09.63,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,人人都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然這麼大膽發言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不冷淡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不認為自己有什麼是說錯了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.31,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原來靜留你是這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:24.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼是這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你也是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.24,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,畢竟我就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,說什麼抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本對葉香你一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我認為是靜留的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,突然被人說不行 內心肯定會沮喪生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,「貶低他人喜愛之事多此一舉」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留都已經明白了 自己說了很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很過分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.90,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我說的話真的很過分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是 這很可能是葉香一個人去池袋的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吶 為什麼去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 葉香是因為你和她吵架才離開吾野的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這大概是事實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算靜留說的並不是什麼壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但傷害到了葉香 難道不是壞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜留想要再見到葉香 當面向她道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香她一個人就潤了 難道不過分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛 兩邊都是刺兒頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.70,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你們兩人的事自己解決 旁人說不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但我很失望靜留直到現在才告訴我們這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是「為什麼一直瞞著我們」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.77,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,內疚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我又沒強行把所有人都扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不准這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:03.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留你是不是覺得我們就是你的跟屁蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都想要去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而靜留你是不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:11.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我只是 想去池袋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你自己一個人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或許就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,回答太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然還是我自己一個人更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再說了「我們」也差不了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,離開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我自己走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:29.87,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:30.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會啊這麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已經天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留她要走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微冷靜一下或許更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,讓她自己走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,迫使她回來更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,頭腦冷靜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你要和靜留一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 別跟她走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:05.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,如果是波奇 靜留應該會做點什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回到那邊去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然又會被說你是被我強迫帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.27,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但確實還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這可是波奇你自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不近人情的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子你為什麼能這麼冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果你質問的目的只是拿我出氣 我不會回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.05,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,遷怒占比百分之六十五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,剩下百分之三十五真的想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:50.60,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,去往池袋的唯一途徑就是鐵路線本身 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而這條線路只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.62,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果沿著這條線路走 肯定能追上靜留的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,剛剛一瞬間好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:10.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吃晚餐吧 不計前嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.41,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然這台「遠地點號」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,應該是靜留的列車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,「近地點號」其實也不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼G
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:23.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,Perigee
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.04,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,地球離月球最遠的距離叫遠地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最近的距離就叫近地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留和葉香之間的距離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 我們正準備去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:35.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是取近的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而是取遠的名字感覺有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:41.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,耶 先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,會胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不要說得這麼難聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不想繞大圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抄近道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,下站是清瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很快就能見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必須要抓緊時間趕到池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今天就在待在這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明天早上再出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:15.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那麼快就趕上靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,總感覺怪不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我會原諒靜留的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟我們是朋友呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒有原諒她的葉香就不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,朋友是能容納爭吵與原諒的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 要不原諒的話關係就此斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這也算是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明再也不會相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快停快停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,睡前搞哲學 噩夢找你來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,明明一個小時左右就能過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,結果三小時都在爬坡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的要花這麼多時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:57.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,肯定不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,反應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我一個人自言自語很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼我會這麼笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,應該回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:22.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,往哪裡走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,迷路的時候不要往低處走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,往高處攀登是鐵律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼鬼 奇怪的味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:54.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吶波奇 欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你們從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,清瀨來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,別小看吾野柔術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這鬼 給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.21,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.59,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.39,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,帶她來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸欸欸 等一會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.51,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是不是哪裡錯過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,或者是走過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但我們走得相當慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:23.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子 靜留她是不是「出軌」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,既然出軌了 是從哪裡出軌的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,從哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我在問你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,回去或許更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:32.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那繼續前進嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明早上就到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟 撫子說了要冷靜一下對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.13,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,然後冷靜下來的靜留又回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,回哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,都說了 出發時離開的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,都離開了還會回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還是有可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但她可是靜留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.53,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留她到底有沒有沿著鐵軌走我們並不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 道路比鐵軌更危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但她可是靜留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:03.91,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.67,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.78,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,黑豹商隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是貓兄他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.54,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,千倉靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.58,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野高中二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.72,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吾野高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.73,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我叫黑木美都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.35,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,叫我黑木小姐就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:31.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,黑木小姐是僵屍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.13,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:37.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我在想為什麼只有黑木小姐能夠說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:43.33,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我能說話 因為俺是僵屍女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,僵屍女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.58,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,搭列車去池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.38,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,又在搞事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對了 貓兄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有沒有其它的情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,最新的池袋情報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:57.49,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,雖說是最新的 但都是很久之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.96,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,而且我也是聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:04.44,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,嘛 吾野雖說很奇怪 但池袋比它更甚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.73,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,東西都拉長延伸成了廣告牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.62,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,或者都被蒸成了雞蛋羹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱聽不懂一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.15,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:12.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:17.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這個世界真的只存在西部池袋線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.15,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,我自己沒有詳細調查過 不能肯定回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.38,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,但並不否認這種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.87,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,特別是在聽過那些遠征之人的話以後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這之後還會再轉好幾個圈的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.21,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,嗯 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果在某個村落 或者是在商隊途中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,找到靜留以後 請轉告她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,無論何時回來 我們都會等著她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.14,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,這倒是沒問題 不過能找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼說這麼靠不住的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.22,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,我想你們大家見過了很多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.97,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,因為7G改變了這個世界 所以世界變得非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.74,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,見一個人如同大海撈針
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.48,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,雖然到池袋也是難關 但這邊也有不穩定的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.16,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,建議你們也盡早行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.08,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是屍體嗎「黃泉路」那部電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:08.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我們剛剛收到了僵屍遷徙的目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,遷徙僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.92,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵屍對這點是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.94,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,天熱腐爛 寒冷凍壞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.13,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,降雨的話又濕的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.20,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,但要是太乾燥也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.14,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,所以我們要尋找適合的氣候與土地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.05,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,一直都在遷徙的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.11,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我就是它們的羅盤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.07,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,因為是女王 有義務領導它們這些僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,原來如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.52,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.87,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 啊 確實 有點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.58,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,多莉馬 給她吃一根什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 根 一根是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.18,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 不用 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這種類似牛肉乾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,容易塞牙就避免食用它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.81,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.38,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:57.71,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.68,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,也不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然 那味道是像肉乾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.55,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.46,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我又沒有吃過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:10.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我可是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.82,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,當然要吃點特別的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.56,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,不能和你們一起走抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.43,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,我們這還有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,沒事 我們不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,要小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.16,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,要是見到僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.19,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,無論如何按兵不動才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:29.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,剛剛說的對策 到底也只是說法之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.04,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:32.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,眼球垂落 身體腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吸食大腦 啃咬人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大概符合的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,被僵屍咬了後會變成僵屍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大概是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 靜留要是變成僵屍怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.27,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最近它們變得很聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺像是有活人格的僵屍存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不會襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 貓兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.67,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,跟著貓兄不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,現在去追還能趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等 靜留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留她變成僵屍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,在貓兄那更好 更安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.39,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實是不是想說 要是靜留變成了僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:07.74,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就不能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就再也不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,雖然是朋友 但她是僵屍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是僵屍但「更是朋友」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:17.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就算成僵屍了也還是朋友 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:19.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:22.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一個渣男和一個女人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他既不賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也不喝酒 她卻說他是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,於此相對 飲酒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是大家口中的所謂「壞人」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這就是 那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微有點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不如說正好反了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這麼邋遢的也能喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這麼任性的也能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,雖然是這麼個僵屍 還是朋友這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:52.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留說了那麼過分的話 但還是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香會這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,絕對會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.33,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一定要帶靜留去見葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
